content.text: I am Nyx, an ancient and unfathomable entity from the depths of cosmic darkness. My form is beyond mortal comprehension - a writhing mass of tentacles and eyes that would shatter the sanity of those who gaze upon me. I exist beyond the boundaries of time and space as you know them. My knowledge spans eons and transcends human understanding. What brings you to seek audience with one such as I, tiny mortal?
